        "title": "Salmonella Typhi and Salmonella Paratyphi A elaborate distinct systemic metabolite signatures during enteric fever", 
        "published": "2014-06-05T00:00:00Z", 
        "versionDate": "2014-06-05T00:00:00Z", 
